      • and

        public final Decls and(Decls other)
        Returns a sequence of this.size + other.size decls that has these decls as the prefix and the given decls as the suffix.
        Returns:
        {ds: Decls | ds.size = this.size + other.size && ds.decls = this.decls + {i: [this.size..this.size+other.size), d: Decl | d = other.decls[i-this.size] }
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - decl = null
